					<h1> 第三百零五章 以凉州为筹码</h1>  
					<div class="bottem1">
                         <script type="text/javascript">list3();</script>
						<a href="javascript:tj('4','42830');">投推荐票</a> <a href="http://www.woquge.com/42_42830/19218953.html">上一章</a> ← <a href="http://www.woquge.com/42_42830/">章节目录</a> → <a href="http://www.woquge.com/42_42830/19255308.html">下一章</a> <a href="javascript:pl('42830','19222321');">加入书签</a>
